snippet.title: Farming Simulator 25: Cinematic Trailer (Announcement)
snippet.description:
See what's in store for Farming Simulator.

It's real! 🤯
Farming Simulator 25 will come this year, November 12th.
For PC, Mac, Playstation 5 and Xbox Series X/S.
Pre-order now! https://www.farming-simulator.com/buy-now.php?&platform=pc

🚜 Want more Farming Simulator?
